00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:20.180 align:middle line:84%
>> Like the other day I
was walking at my home

00:00:20.180 --> 00:00:23.840 align:middle line:84%
in California, and I looked over
the fence and there were these

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:25.220 align:middle line:90%
exquisite--

00:00:25.220 --> 00:00:29.720 align:middle line:84%
the whole fence was covered with
these beautiful blue flowers.

00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:31.250 align:middle line:90%
And I was in ecstasy.

00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:36.340 align:middle line:84%
They were radiantly
bright and blue.

00:00:36.340 --> 00:00:37.510 align:middle line:90%
I didn't have my glasses on.

00:00:37.510 --> 00:00:38.840 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know what kind
of flowers they were,

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:40.640 align:middle line:84%
but they were just
absolutely beautiful.

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:42.090 align:middle line:90%
And I was just in delight.

00:00:42.090 --> 00:00:45.140 align:middle line:10%
And I went to my neighbor with--

00:00:45.140 --> 00:00:47.390 align:middle line:10%
on whose estate I
live, and I said,

00:00:47.390 --> 00:00:50.600 align:middle line:10%
there are just these absolutely
beautiful blue flowers.

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:53.270 align:middle line:90%


00:00:53.270 --> 00:00:56.792 align:middle line:84%
And then later in
the afternoon, we

00:00:56.792 --> 00:00:58.500 align:middle line:84%
started to go outside
for something else.

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:00.690 align:middle line:84%
I said, oh, let me show
you these blue flowers.

00:01:00.690 --> 00:01:05.090 align:middle line:84%
And I came up and there weren't
any blue flowers, because they

00:01:05.090 --> 00:01:06.590 align:middle line:90%
were morning glories.

00:01:06.590 --> 00:01:09.380 align:middle line:84%
And those of you that
know about morning glories

00:01:09.380 --> 00:01:12.800 align:middle line:84%
know that they're only
glorious in the morning.

00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:18.770 align:middle line:84%
And at first I felt confused,
and angry, and upset,

00:01:18.770 --> 00:01:20.240 align:middle line:90%
and embarrassed, and everything.

00:01:20.240 --> 00:01:23.400 align:middle line:84%
I said, I could have sworn
there were blue flowers here.

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:27.300 align:middle line:84%
And then he said, You
mean the morning glories?

00:01:27.300 --> 00:01:30.120 align:middle line:84%
And then the word
morning glory went in,

00:01:30.120 --> 00:01:33.150 align:middle line:84%
and I thought, ah, that's
what morning glory means.

00:01:33.150 --> 00:01:34.465 align:middle line:90%
Ah, what do you know?

00:01:34.465 --> 00:01:35.265 align:middle line:90%
And I relaxed.

00:01:35.265 --> 00:01:40.800 align:middle line:90%


00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:43.920 align:middle line:84%
Faith is understanding that
they are morning glories.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:48.000 align:middle line:84%
Faith is understanding
that as long as there

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:52.530 align:middle line:84%
are any clingings in you
at all, that you are going

00:01:52.530 --> 00:01:57.720 align:middle line:84%
to lose the spiritual
material aspects

00:01:57.720 --> 00:02:01.950 align:middle line:84%
of spiritual experience,
which is understanding,

00:02:01.950 --> 00:02:05.760 align:middle line:84%
bliss, rapture,
feeling of intimacy.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:10.350 align:middle line:84%
Anything that is an experience
connected with spirituality

00:02:10.350 --> 00:02:12.430 align:middle line:90%
is going to come and go.

00:02:12.430 --> 00:02:16.000 align:middle line:84%
To the extent that you
have based your faith

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.160 align:middle line:90%
on experience--

00:02:18.160 --> 00:02:20.860 align:middle line:90%
this is a really far out edge--

00:02:20.860 --> 00:02:24.700 align:middle line:84%
you are bound to have a hard
road, because you're going

00:02:24.700 --> 00:02:26.590 align:middle line:90%
to constantly be flickering.

00:02:26.590 --> 00:02:30.880 align:middle line:84%
And you're going to be afraid of
the shifts of your experience.

00:02:30.880 --> 00:02:34.750 align:middle line:84%
