that faith concerns something

00:02:34.750 --> 00:02:39.490 align:middle line:84%
that lies behind experience,
that is just being,

00:02:39.490 --> 00:02:42.790 align:middle line:84%
not the experience of
being, but just being.

00:02:42.790 --> 00:02:48.220 align:middle line:84%
That when it turns dull
and it all seems empty

00:02:48.220 --> 00:02:54.690 align:middle line:84%
and there's nobody around,
it's much more of awesome.

00:02:54.690 --> 00:02:59.830 align:middle line:84%
And then it opens
up and it's awesome.

00:02:59.830 --> 00:03:03.965 align:middle line:84%
And you don't demand of yourself
that you always be wise,

00:03:03.965 --> 00:03:06.550 align:middle line:84%
that you always be
clear, and you always

00:03:06.550 --> 00:03:09.380 align:middle line:84%
feel like you're
connected to God.

00:03:09.380 --> 00:03:13.010 align:middle line:84%
That you realize that all these
experiences are just the way

00:03:13.010 --> 00:03:16.310 align:middle line:84%
the mind is playing in
the universe of form.

00:03:16.310 --> 00:03:21.200 align:middle line:84%
And that when you're feeling
that intimacy, and that warmth,

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:24.630 align:middle line:84%
and that devotional,
delicious quality,

00:03:24.630 --> 00:03:28.910 align:middle line:84%
if you will go in deeper to
find the place behind all

00:03:28.910 --> 00:03:32.240 align:middle line:84%
that stuff, then you will
find that when you're

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:37.850 align:middle line:84%
in the depressed, cut off, empty
thing, you can sit with that

00:03:37.850 --> 00:03:42.260 align:middle line:90%
and find the place to rest.

00:03:42.260 --> 00:03:45.260 align:middle line:84%
It's not an experience
of negative or positive.

00:03:45.260 --> 00:03:46.240 align:middle line:90%
It's just mm.

00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:48.880 align:middle line:90%


00:03:48.880 --> 00:03:55.090 align:middle line:84%
